      </svg>
      <div class="footer-trust-text">
        <strong>30-DAY RETURNS</strong>
        <span>Shop with confidence with 30-day returns on eligible pieces.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-trust-item">
      <svg width="38" height="38" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#c5a880" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <path d="M2 17h2m4 0h8m4 0h2" />
        <path d="M2 17V5a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h11v13" />
        <path d="M14 7h5.5a1 1 0 0 1 .8.4l2.5 3.1a1 1 0 0 1 .2.5V17h-5" />
        <circle cx="6" cy="17" r="2" />
        <circle cx="18" cy="17" r="2" />
      </svg>
      <div class="footer-trust-text">
        <strong>FREE INSURED DELIVERY</strong>
        <span>Tracked and insured delivery for added peace of mind.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-trust-item">
      <svg width="38" height="38" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#c5a880" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
        <path d="M9.5 9h5l1.5 2.5-4 4.5-4-4.5L9.5 9z"/>
        <path d="M9.5 9l2.5 2.5 2.5-2.5"/>
        <path d="M12 11.5v4.5"/>
      </svg>
      <div class="footer-trust-text">
        <strong>LIMITED LIFETIME WARRANTY</strong>
        <span>Our craftsmanship is backed by a limited lifetime warranty.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-trust-item">
      <svg width="38" height="38" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#c5a880" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <rect x="5" y="10" width="14" height="11" rx="2"/>
        <path d="M8 10V7a4 4 0 0 1 8 0v3"/>
        <circle cx="12" cy="14.5" r="1.5"/>
        <path d="M12 16v2"/>
      </svg>
      <div class="footer-trust-text">
        <strong>SECURE PAYMENTS</strong>
        <span>Safe and secure checkout with trusted payment methods.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

